560
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:41,020
 evropske novce metro.

561
00:36:41,740 --> 00:36:42,860
 Solun je svoje otvorio

562
00:36:42,860 --> 00:36:44,680
 za Novu godinu.

563
00:36:44,680 --> 00:36:45,320
 A Solun,

564
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,000
 i onda neko kaže

565
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,460
 mi smo pre mali,

566
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:49,400
 a Solun nema ni 300.000 stanovnika.

567
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:51,420
 Zagreb je jedan od većih gradova

568
00:36:51,420 --> 00:36:52,120
 bez metrova.

569
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:52,840
 Znate,

570
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:54,960
 u države u Evropi

571
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:55,600
 koje nemaju metro

572
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:56,200
 su bivše,

573
