 to su eksi

574
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:58,700
 Jugoslavijske države

575
00:36:58,700 --> 00:36:59,920
 i Albanije.

576
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:00,880
 I mi ćemo ostati

577
00:37:00,880 --> 00:37:01,580
 u toj čakuri.

578
00:37:01,580 --> 00:37:02,920
 Pa to je ono što sam rekao,

579
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,020
 Zagrebu treba

580
00:37:04,020 --> 00:37:05,300
 gradonačni koji ima viziju,

581
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:06,800
 ali koji ima snage donijeti

582
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:08,000
 odluku i izvesti je do kraja.

583
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:08,720
 Znači,

584
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:09,320
 to nije,

585
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:09,860
 međutim,

586
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:11,200
 kad je u pitanju

587
00:37:11,200 --> 00:37:12,440
 izgradnja lake željeznice,

588
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:14,040
 bit će vidljivi rezultati

589
00:37:14,040 --> 00:37:14,920
 u prvom mandatu.

590
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,720
 Jer postoji

591
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:16,840
 nadzemna trasa,

592
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:18,200
 devet i nešto kilometara,

593
00:37:18,200 --> 00:37:18,780
 Kvatrić,

594
00:37:18,780 --> 00:37:19,980
 Zračna luka,

595
00:37:19,980 --> 00:37:20,440
 Zagreb,

596
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:21,820
 koja se može vrlo lako

597
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:23,060
 realizirati u jednom mandatu.

598
00:37:23,060 --> 00:37:24,300
 Krenatome,

599
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:25,960
 nije to tako,

600
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,000
 međutim...

601
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:27,860
 A mogu predposljati

602
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:28,740
 da će biti kaos

603
00:37:28,740 --> 00:37:29,400
 na tim mjestima

604
00:37:29,400 --> 00:37:30,500
 gdje se to bude gradilo,

605
00:37:30,500 --> 00:37:31,480
 da će to biti...

606
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:33,820
 neće biti...

607
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:34,820
 Ali treba...

608
00:37:34,820 --> 00:37:35,720
 Neće biti...

609
00:37:35,720 --> 00:37:37,220
 Mi možemo se bojati kaosa.

610
00:37:37,220 --> 00:37:38,180
 Sjećate se one priče

611
00:37:38,180 --> 00:37:38,960
 da će biti kaos

612
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,200
 kad se bude gradio

613
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:41,040
 Zagrebučki rotor?

614
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:42,800
 Sjećate se te priče?

615
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:44,020
 Pa godinu dana

616
00:37:44,020 --> 00:37:45,000
 se pumpalo u medijima

617
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:45,720
 da će biti kaos.

618
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:46,820
 Ako se dobro organizira,

619
00:37:46,820 --> 00:37:47,720
 kaosa nije bilo.

620
00:37:47,720 --> 00:37:49,140
 A onda je Tomašević

621
00:37:49,140 --> 00:37:50,280
 četiri godine

622
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:51,340
 objavljao,

623
00:37:51,340 --> 00:37:52,060
 obnavljao

624
00:37:52,060 --> 00:37:53,740
 Jadranski most,

625
00:37:53,740 --> 00:37:54,620
 pa je bio kaos.

626
00:37:54,620 --> 00:37:55,800
 Se ovisi kako

627
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,160
 tko vodi poslovi,

628
00:37:57,160 --> 00:37:57,700
 kako ih organiziraju.

629
00:37:57,700 --> 00:38:00,220
 Ja bih radije imao kaos

630
00:38:00,220 --> 00:38:01,040
 da moje djete

631
00:38:01,040 --> 00:38:01,700
