634
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:04,460
 kako spada.

635
00:38:04,460 --> 00:38:05,260
 Ja sam spreman

636
00:38:05,260 --> 00:38:06,180
 napraviti taj rizik,

637
00:38:06,180 --> 00:38:08,320
 ali ne znam jeste li

638
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:08,700
