640
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:11,040
 Ja se toga ne boli.

641
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:12,300
 Kako bih rekao,

642
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:13,080
 dosta je složeno,

643
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:13,460
 znate,

644
00:38:13,460 --> 00:38:14,000
 mislim,

645
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:14,300
 vjerujem,

646
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:15,240
 zna da je puno bolje

647
00:38:15,240 --> 00:38:15,380
 neko je.

648
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:17,380
 Složeno je za onoga

649
00:38:17,380 --> 00:38:17,980
 koji, recimo,

650
00:38:17,980 --> 00:38:18,720
 za Tomaševića

651
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:19,360
