652
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:21,220
 Pa vidite,

653
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,340
 pogledajte bolnicu

654
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:22,920
 Srebrenjak,

655
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,560
 63 miliona eura

656
00:38:24,560 --> 00:38:25,420
 evropskog novca.

657
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:27,020
 Započeti radovi.

658
