 niti jedan posto projekta.

662
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:31,880
 Ma to je sugo.

663
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:33,860
 Jer izvođaš radova mi je rekao,

664
00:38:33,860 --> 00:38:34,460
 mi nismo imali

665
00:38:34,460 --> 00:38:34,940
 s druge strane

666
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:35,720
 s kim razgovarati.

667
00:38:35,720 --> 00:38:37,540
 A vi kad gradite,

668
00:38:37,540 --> 00:38:39,860
 gradite kuću doma,

669
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:40,820
 pa uzmite majstora,

670
00:38:40,820 --> 00:38:42,480
 ali on isto investitora,

671
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:43,600
 ono koji gradi,

672
00:38:43,600 --> 00:38:44,300
 mora pitati

673
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,000
 svaki dan

674
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:46,460
 za neki detalj.

675
00:38:46,460 --> 00:38:47,060
 A vi ako imate

676
00:38:47,060 --> 00:38:47,640
 neznalice

677
00:38:47,640 --> 00:38:48,260
 i nesposobne

678
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:48,960
 s druge strane,

679
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:49,860
 onda naravno

680
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:50,640
 ne možete realizirati

681
00:38:50,640 --> 00:38:51,320
 niti jedan projekta.

682
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,160
 Vrlo je,

683
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:53,560
 a zašto mi se da Sofija

684
00:38:53,560 --> 00:38:54,760
 može sagraditi

685
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:55,800
 pozivnu željenicu,

686
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,140
 a da Zagreb ne može?

687
00:38:57,140 --> 00:38:58,380
 A bili smo

688
00:38:58,380 --> 00:38:59,460
 Bugarskoj uvijek u uzor.

689
00:38:59,460 --> 00:39:00,240
 Ovdje su dolazili

690
00:39:00,240 --> 00:39:01,320
 i učiti i studirati

691
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,600
 i razumijete.

692
00:39:02,600 --> 00:39:04,400
 To je absurdno

693
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:05,860
 i to nije

694
00:39:05,860 --> 00:39:07,700
 izgovor

695
00:39:07,700 --> 00:39:09,800
 za one koji znaju

696
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:10,780
 i koji umiju.

697
00:39:10,780 --> 00:39:12,200
 Ako mogu ja samo

698
00:39:12,200 --> 00:39:12,960
 isto me nemojte

699
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:13,780
 krivo shvatiti,

700
00:39:13,780 --> 00:39:14,420
 ali kad je,

701
00:39:14,420 --> 00:39:15,260
 ja znam da vi

702
00:39:15,260 --> 00:39:16,140
 niste bandići,

703
00:39:16,140 --> 00:39:17,100
 ali kad je u pitanju

704
00:39:17,100 --> 00:39:18,360
 gradnja metroa

705
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:19,160
 i tako velikih

706
00:39:19,160 --> 00:39:19,760
 prometnih

707
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:21,020
 infrastrukturnih stvari,

708
00:39:21,020 --> 00:39:22,420
 ne može mi ne doći

709
00:39:22,420 --> 00:39:22,760
 na um

710
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,500
 i onaj argument

711
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:24,080
 koji često

712
00:39:24,080 --> 00:39:25,360
 i aktualna vlast koristi,

713
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:25,980
 a to je da

714
00:39:25,980 --> 00:39:27,700
 bandić u šest mandata

715
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:28,500
