719
00:39:32,640 --> 00:39:33,520
 ajmo reći,

720
00:39:33,520 --> 00:39:35,160
 iz kruga bandićevih ljudi

721
00:39:35,160 --> 00:39:36,440
 napravio jedan metro.

722
00:39:36,440 --> 00:39:36,940
 Ja, znate,

723
00:39:36,940 --> 00:39:38,320
 ja mogu reći sljedeće,

724
00:39:40,780 --> 00:39:42,140
 21. neposredno

725
00:39:42,140 --> 00:39:42,760
 pred izbore,

726
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:43,800
 Tomašević gostuje

727
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:45,460
 na javnoj televiziji

728
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:46,240
 nedeljom u dva

729
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,820
 i mrtvo hladno kaže

730
00:39:47,820 --> 00:39:48,640
 da će početi

731
00:39:48,640 --> 00:39:49,560
 graditi metro

732
00:39:49,560 --> 00:39:50,860
 u mandatu.

733
00:39:50,860 --> 00:39:52,480
 Prvo, prošao mandat

734
00:39:52,480 --> 00:39:54,160
