 ovih cestoanih?

741
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:05,680
 Ima pet.

742
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:07,380
 A od tih pet

743
00:40:07,380 --> 00:40:08,100
 jedan ipoli

744
00:40:08,100 --> 00:40:09,060
 sagradio bandić.

745
