748
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:15,760
 A onda vam je

749
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:16,760
 od tog domovinskog

750
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:19,140
 pa do ovamo,

751
00:40:19,140 --> 00:40:20,400
 do Hanjslove

752
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,180
 i do Slavonske

753
00:40:21,180 --> 00:40:21,860
 sagradio

754
00:40:21,860 --> 00:40:23,280
 novi ulaz u grad

755
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:24,280
 Radničku

756
00:40:24,280 --> 00:40:25,980
 kojom se diše.

757
00:40:25,980 --> 00:40:26,680
 Samo o tome,

758
00:40:26,680 --> 00:40:27,840
 kad pogleda

759
00:40:27,840 --> 00:40:29,440
 sve denivelacije

760
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:30,340
 i taj tamo

761
00:40:30,340 --> 00:40:30,960
 Hanjslava,

762
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:31,960
 Slavonska

763
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:33,680
 i Slavonska,

764
00:40:33,680 --> 00:40:34,220
 Ljudevita,

765
00:40:34,220 --> 00:40:34,940
 Posavskog

766
00:40:34,940 --> 00:40:35,680
 i Savska,

767
00:40:35,680 --> 00:40:37,360
 Slavonska,

768
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:38,220
 odnosno Zagrebaška,

769
00:40:38,220 --> 00:40:39,340
 sve to sagradio bandić.

770
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:40,680
 proširio je Zagrebašku.

771
00:40:40,680 --> 00:40:41,460
 A zamislite,

772
00:40:41,460 --> 00:40:43,400
 znači Jankomirski most

773
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:44,680
 je bio dvotračni,

774
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:45,260
 on je sagradio

775
00:40:45,260 --> 00:40:46,040
 još jedan pored njega,

776
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:46,560
 ovaj obnovio

777
00:40:46,560 --> 00:40:47,480
 i sagradio domovinski.

778
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,740
 I imate između

779
00:40:48,740 --> 00:40:49,940
 još samo tri mosta.

780
00:40:49,940 --> 00:40:52,500
 Kad pogledate

781
00:40:52,500 --> 00:40:54,080
 recimo obrazovne objekte,

782
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:55,120
 u bandićevom mandatu

783
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:56,040
 se sagradila

784
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:57,620
 trećina škola

785
00:40:57,620 --> 00:40:58,340
 vrtića

786
00:40:58,340 --> 00:40:59,060
 i sportskih dvora.

787
00:40:59,060 --> 00:41:02,580
 Od šest

788
00:41:02,580 --> 00:41:03,600
 zatvorenih bazena

789
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:04,440
 koje je grad Zagreb

790
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:04,700
 ima,

791
00:41:04,700 --> 00:41:05,700
 tri su sagrađena

792
00:41:05,700 --> 00:41:06,840
 u mom mandatu

793
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:07,980
 kao proširnika za sport,

794
00:41:07,980 --> 00:41:08,920
 znači i u bandićem.

795
00:41:08,920 --> 00:41:10,060
 Ja vodio rada.

796
00:41:10,060 --> 00:41:12,280
 Sagradilo se užasno puno toga,

797
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:12,960
 ali ljudi kao,

798
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:15,260
 mislim,

799
00:41:15,260 --> 00:41:16,900
 ljudi zaboravljaju,

800
00:41:16,900 --> 00:41:17,820
 a onda,

801
00:41:17,820 --> 00:41:19,840
 ali Tomaševiš to jako dobro zna,

802
00:41:19,940 --> 00:41:20,360
 međutim,

803
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:20,820
 on to

804
00:41:20,820 --> 00:41:23,700
 gura po tepih

805
00:41:23,700 --> 00:41:24,340
 i skriva

806
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:26,020
 i sad ću vam reći

807
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:27,540
 kad spominjemo tramvaje.

808
00:41:27,540 --> 00:41:30,020
 U vrijeme bandića

809
00:41:30,020 --> 00:41:30,640
 su kupljene

810
00:41:30,640 --> 00:41:32,660
 142 nova tramvaje,

811
00:41:32,660 --> 00:41:33,860
